# Next_Word_Predictor

## Workflows

1. Update config.yaml
2. Update secrets.yaml [optional]
3. Update params.yaml
4. Update the entity
5. Update the congiguration manager in src code
6. Update the components
7. Update the pipeline
8. Update the main.py
10. app.py

# How to run?

### STEPS:

Clone the repository

```bash
https://github.com/2654Ankit/Next_Word_Predictor
```

### STEP 01 - Create a conda enviroment after opening the repo

```bash
conda create -n nextword python=3.11.3
```

```bash
conda activate nextword
```
### STEP 02 - install the requirements 
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
